reviewText: This is better than a great cup of black coffee!  It's a wake up call for American Christians.  The video is eighty minutes long, but worth seeing it through to the end.  The subject matter is very serious and presented with conviction, yet there is the freshness that only can come from Ken Ham. This is not a science lecture it is about the relevance of scripture as touching earthly things and the absolute importance of the first eleven chapters of Genesis.
